<section class="az-faq" id="faq" aria-labelledby="FaqTitle-{{ section.id }}" data-faq>
  <div class="page-width az-faq__container">
    <div class="az-faq__header">
      <div class="az-faq__eyebrow">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</div>
      <h2 class="az-faq__title" id="FaqTitle-{{ section.id }}">Everything you need to know</h2>
      <p class="az-faq__desc">Discover answers about Aromazur fragrances, inspired by the perfumery heritage of Grasse and crafted with French luxury traditions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="az-faq__list" role="list">
      <div class="az-faq__item is-open" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          <span>What makes Aromazur fragrances unique?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region">
          <p>Aromazur embodies the refined elegance of the French Riviera, where timeless sophistication meets modern artistry. Each creation is inspired by the perfumery heritage of Grasse and reflects a delicate balance of nature, emotion, and savoir‑faire. Crafted with care and guided by French luxury traditions, our perfumes are designed to leave a lasting impression — subtle yet unforgettable, radiant yet deeply personal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="az-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Are your fragrances inspired by Grasse?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region" hidden>
          <p>Yes. Aromazur draws inspiration from Grasse, the perfumery capital of the world. Each fragrance reflects centuries of French perfumery artistry, combining natural essences with modern innovation. Our creations honor the delicate balance of nature, emotion, and savoir‑faire that defines the Grasse tradition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="az-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How do I choose the right fragrance?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region" hidden>
          <p>Browse our collections inspired by the French Riviera and Grasse heritage. Each fragrance is crafted to evoke a distinct mood and environment. If you’d like personalized guidance, contact our team — we’re here to help you discover the perfect scent for your space and style.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="az-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What is your shipping policy?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region" hidden>
          <p>We ship most orders within 24 hours (business days). Delivery typically takes 2–4 days within the continental US. You will receive tracking information as soon as your order ships. Free shipping is available on orders over €100.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="az-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What is your return policy?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region" hidden>
          <p>We offer a 30‑day satisfaction guarantee. If you are not completely happy with your purchase, contact our support team and we will process a return or exchange. Returns are free and simple — we will guide you through every step.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="az-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="az-faq__q" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Are your fragrances safe and clean?</span>
          <span class="az-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="az-faq__a" role="region" hidden>
          <p>Our fragrances are formulated with quality ingredients and created with care. If you have sensitivities or specific concerns, please reach out — we’re happy to help you choose the best option for your needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

